Raw Cookie Dough
source|
url|http://www.grouprecipes.com/66660/ok-to-eat-raw-cookie-dough.html#
aliases|
tags|
activeTime|
totalTime|
yield|
description|edible raw cookie dough. NO EGGS!

# ingredients
[Type A]
5|oz|butter or margarine
6|oz|sugar
3|oz|brown sugar
6|oz|flour
1|tsp|vanilla extract
||Chocolate chips
[Type B]
2 1/4|cup|butter or margarine
2 1/2|cup|sugar
3/4|cup|brown sugar
2 1/2|cup|flour
2|tsp|vanilla extract
||Chocolate chips

# instructions
Mix up the sugars and butter in a bowl
Add the rest of the ingredients
Enjoy!
Stick it in the fridge with some plastic wrap if you have leftovers.
